95
00:09:37,936 --> 00:09:40,002
You can just cut the chain, okay?

96
00:09:42,691 --> 00:09:46,759
Please. I'm begging you, please.

97
00:09:48,781 --> 00:09:51,346
No, no, no!

98
00:09:57,498 --> 00:10:00,564
Please. Please!

99
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:16,580
