a synthetic version of it.

314
00:37:21,641 --> 00:37:23,497
I didn't realize that
they'd succeeded.

315
00:37:24,685 --> 00:37:26,792
If it really is C.P.H.4,

316
00:37:27,355 --> 00:37:30,629
